}



Controller *--> View
Controller *--> models 
View *--> models
View ..> Mensssages
View ..> index : ACTUALIZA 
index --> Controller : EVENTOS
Controller --> controllers :GET, POST, PUT, DELETE
controllers ..> servis
servis ..> model

HumanPlayer ..> Board
ComputerPlayer ..> Board
Players *--> HumanPlayer
Players *--> ComputerPlayer



@enduml